 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">What is Memrise?</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Memrise is a language learning platform that focuses on building vocabulary through spaced repetition and immersive video content. Founded in 2010, the platform has evolved from a simple flashcard app into a comprehensive language tool. It uses "Learn with Locals" videos to show how native speakers actually talk in real life.</p>
 
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The core philosophy of Memrise is that language learning should be fun and based on how our brains naturally remember things. By using short, engaging video clips and game-like exercises, Memrise aims to make English learning feel less like work and more like a hobby.</p>

