 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Key Features</h2>
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3 text-white">1. Learn with Locals</h3>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">This is the standout feature of Memrise. Instead of listening to robotic voices, you watch thousands of short video clips of real people speaking English in their home cities. This helps you understand different accents, body language, and the natural rhythm of the language.</p>

 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3 text-white">2. Spaced Repetition System (SRS)</h3>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Memrise uses a scientifically proven algorithm to show you words just as you are about to forget them. This ensures that the vocabulary you learn moves from your short-term memory into your long-term memory efficiently.</p>

 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3 text-white">3. MemBot (AI Tutor)</h3>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The new MemBot feature allows you to practice conversations with an AI tutor. You can choose different scenarios, such as checking into a hotel or ordering coffee, and practice your speaking and writing in a low-pressure environment.</p>

 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Memrise Pricing</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Memrise offers a free version and a "Memrise Pro" subscription. The free version gives you access to basic courses, but the Pro version is required for the best features.</p>
