 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Verdict: Is it Worth it?</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Memrise is one of the best tools for beginners and intermediate learners who want to build a strong foundation of vocabulary and listening skills. The "Learn with Locals" videos are a game-changer for understanding natural English. However, if you are looking for deep grammar study or high-level academic English, you might need to pair Memrise with a more formal course or a 1-on-1 tutor on a platform like Preply.</p>

